Jaradis Stormcaller 40th Shaman<br><br><i>People demand freedom of speech as a compensation for the freedom of thought  which they seldom use.</i> - Soren Kierkegaard</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uretiredjustise.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RetiredJustise</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.justise.com/bf.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/5/01 11:59:45 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.justise.com/j.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ToV</span><hr size=1> It doesn't exactly work that way.<br>
<br>
There's an area inside thats sorta like a welcome area, it has a bunch of mobs on CoV that sorta wander around and make the place pretty.<br>
<br>
Then if you take a right, you get to the testing halls, 2 KoS bad moffo wurms, your expedition is stoped short that way.<br>
<br>
If you go straight ahead, there is a door with a hallway area and some rooms. All the rooms have kos not on cov mofo's and the hall leads to a very nasty wyvern not on cov. So your trip that way is ended, if you go left, you get to go to a cov faction area with mobs and stuff, and at the end is a dragon that gives out quests for the test area.  <br>
<br>
So basicly you can only document 1/3 of the area, you can drag the red wyvern in the hall out of the hall and into the non-kos area, then go past him which there is an area with some kos mobs that dont see invis, but you don't get to go very far before they start to see again. <br>
<br>
In which case you run into a BIG ass red dragon right on the edge of a fuggin CLIFF, and then within sight of that dragon is another dragon to his right with 2 body guard wurms.<br>
<br>
Thats about as far as I was able to explore. =/ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=bolrusspiritwalker>Bolrus Spiritwalker</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_purplespot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 131<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/7/01 6:08:43 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   tips</span><hr size=1> Two tips:<br>
