<br>
2) The perspicacious mapper will notice that the floor tiles are conveniently 10 /loc units square, and are generally set with square boundaries at the walls. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uretiredjustise.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RetiredJustise</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.justise.com/bf.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/7/01 10:52:14 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.justise.com/j.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: tips</span><hr size=1> Bind sight is bugged right now and you can only cast it if you can see your target. =( <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ulver>Ulver</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Slackershaman</span><br>  Posts: 297<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/7/01 11:05:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: tips</span><hr size=1> Yep Bolrus, the nerf stick hit again. The vision spells can only be chained as long as you have line of sight on your target. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualvimar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alvimar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 190<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/7/01 11:40:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: tips</span><h